{"tid":759141,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家平時點同男/女朋友相處？","createTime":"2018-07-28T10:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T02:05:08.000Z","uid":171272,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"528ea4ecdd258923f68fc0e2a4017fba31494b68","tid":759141,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"我本身無乜安全感 + 幾癡身<br />\n成日都想見到對方/對方陪下我傾計都好<br />\n因為唔係long D 又唔係忙<br />\n所以會期望一個星期可以見一次<br />\n唔需要食貴嘢/去邊度玩<br />\n就算一齊坐一日，行下都已經好滿足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但依家個男朋友基本上一星期真係見得一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次都我約佢<br />\n就算我開到口話自己有咩想做佢都唔會主動約我<br />\n有時見得三四個鐘就話要返屋企<br />\n每次都諸多藉口<br />\n電話又唔會傾<br />\nWhatsapp又愛理不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前就算通頂都會陪我<br />\n依家一分鐘都嫌多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊唔太耐就已經咁<br />\n我自問一直都唔太識同情人相處<br />\n一直以來都係個好遷就得人嘅角色<br />\n好自然今次我都諗 : 係咪自己太高要求？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求大家比啲意見我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">有時真係會覺得拍拖好辛苦好想放棄......</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1f10880ae5d6036040b7baedbd67f66ad965834","tid":759141,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6d95e79d675a2927eb7204493dc612e922b7155","tid":759141,"uid":32721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"三四個鐘扑完就梗係走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e811b002fdb5b85c98ca64ee347e6fbc072e0eb7","tid":759141,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"以前幾忙點到揾一日放  加平日一兩日晚上食飯 陪女朋友  佢都話少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaf9e00eb32abf45ca4f981b0bc0fa3ff9cd6a7","tid":759141,"uid":18568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"無女朋友!<br />\n唔撚知!"},{"pid":"c4a5690dacc47d952c69b374a585f74a77710a58","tid":759141,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d95e79d675a2927eb7204493dc612e922b7155","tid":759141,"uid":32721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"三四個鐘扑完就梗係走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:19:21.000Z","msg":"無扑都走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee432dfef4f6c1e5a26b6aac03462d1db0f80042","tid":759141,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e811b002fdb5b85c98ca64ee347e6fbc072e0eb7","tid":759141,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"以前幾忙點到揾一日放  加平日一兩日晚上食飯 陪女朋友  佢都話少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fc35beef2ccc8725769a96b3810a78aba3e0da","tid":759141,"uid":8243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"以前一星期會見幾次 平日就多數我去接佢收工一齊食晚飯<br />\n但依家佢份工會返到成身汗 但又冇得沖涼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就變咗一星期淨係得六同日會見<br />\n多數星期六日都會見足全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7762c8c9d1dc6deb997b37d8cb7637cca4ecfb1","tid":759141,"uid":152481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"就係因為見面問題最終頂唔順分咗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話寧願見粒籃球好過見我 我真係唔識同男朋友相處 之前亦都一樣 一直以來可能係我問題"},{"pid":"c1cdcd3a96973a08af5f9b795bafb339d120abcc","tid":759141,"uid":77803,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"總會有一個越黎越懶嘅，唔肯努力最尾都係分手架啦，無謂浪費時間"},{"pid":"6cf041ef7776bf5b17dc31ec68b791ae29c37732","tid":759141,"uid":144551,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"平時一有時間就會去陪女朋友接佢收工咁，除非我收得好夜，再攰都會去陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n申利 拍左一年幾"},{"pid":"fc6b057d5b7966c58b65c137c43b76f33bfd9315","tid":759141,"uid":191296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"一星期見2-4日<br />\n一定有1日係見全日<br />\n有1日係一齊食晚飯<br />\n有0-2日係可能整咗啲野畀佢，喺車站等佢，畀佢見一見就走"},{"pid":"8913bce6ce2ff0fd40083e9788c090a1f258164f","tid":759141,"uid":107085,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"一星期見四五日，見到凌晨都唔捨得走<br />\n有心見就點都抽到時間見"},{"pid":"0abba4abf330b2d302801b8e8fb740b602ac8f7a","tid":759141,"uid":75868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"今日先因為呢樣野同女朋友嘈完交<br />\n拍左兩年幾，見面日數越黎越少<br />\n一星期雖然都見到一次，但已經好難係full day<br />\n以前就算見唔到，都可以text下傾計<br />\n而家佢根本係見到先會覆<br />\n好撚心痛，明明自己一直冇變過，但佢的確變左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申唔係帽事"},{"pid":"de00271b78900c8e4c9e9a1eaa8c182dd85bf4e6","tid":759141,"uid":166429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"一星期見三至四日 其中一至兩晚係對方到訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> text得唔算密 但一日會講一至兩次電話 通常夜晚會講長啲 十五分鐘到 自己都幾痴身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常想去邊 一講出黎男友都會話去 因為唔使佢諗節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c2b7476bbd9e338eb83b4